		<title>审计机构辞任导致超微股价大跌</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hans/analysis/market-news/super-micro-slumps-auditor-resignation</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 17:04:43 +0000</pubDate>
